      &lt;img alt="A close-up image of a teenage girl wearing the Fitbit Ace LTE on her wrist." src="https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/ZIEO-BUt_6MfaPmNk-J1vOiNCNU=/0x0:1248x832/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/73514848/Fitbit_Ace_LTE_Lifestyle_Press_Image.0.jpg" /&gt;
