&lt;p id="IjVA2f"&gt;Unlike most smartwatches, the Ace LTE is specifically geared toward children. The durable watch features the same innards as &lt;a href="https://www.theverge.com/23910570/google-pixel-watch-2-review-fitbit-safety-check-battery-stress-tracking"&gt;Google’s Pixel Watch 2&lt;/a&gt; and LTE connectivity, which enables calling, messaging, and real-time location sharing. It also comes with a Tamagotchi-like buddy (nicknamed Eejie) and several wrist-based video games, all of which require children to complete...&lt;/p&gt;
